race.description: Haymans Taree Ladies Day Country Boosted Hcp (Bm58)
race.comment: KING SOLEIL (3) signalled that his next win is not far away with a close second here last time over 1300m. He will be peaking third up, and can go one better this time. SHEILA'S FANTA SEA (4) pushed forward early from a wide gate over 1200m at Scone last start before tiring late to finish fourth/ She cops a wide gate, but won't lack fitness, and she has each-way claims in this. DIAMONDSAREMIO (5) resumed after a six-month break with a solid fifth over 1000m at this track and should appreciate the extra distance, making her a likely top contender. THEDAYTHEMUSICDIED (8) scored third up here 2 weeks ago, and the only surprise was the large price she paid that day. She is only up 1.5kg, and she can repeat the dose, just don't expect another fancy price. BATTLEDANCE (9) ended his last prep as a Kempsey winner when leading all the way. He usually takes a run to get ready, but any market support will be worth following.
